    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With its flawless exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory freshness, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our premier tier of excellence.",
